{"tid":2422670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍威爾伯號駛經台灣海峽　解放軍稱隨時應對一切挑釁","createTime":"2021-02-25T10:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T14:30:59.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9f31062d1e1dac45b014381b576dbdaf6c262422","tid":2422670,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"美軍威爾伯號駛經台灣海峽　解放軍稱隨時應對一切挑釁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577447-20210225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577447-20210225.htm&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=6dbd3ab4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577447-20210225.htm&h=af7a9a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577447-20210225.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍太平洋艦隊公布，伯克級導彈驅逐艦威爾伯號昨日通過台灣海峽，表示是依據國際法的慣常做法，展現美國對自由開放的印太地區的承諾，重申美軍會繼續在國際法容許的情況下，在全球繼續航行及執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍東部戰區新聞發言人張春暉表示，昨日威爾伯號驅逐艦穿過台灣海峽，解放軍東部戰區組織海空兵力，全程進行跟蹤監視，批評美軍船艦的做法，是人為製造台海風險因素，刻意破壞地區和平穩定，中方對此表示堅決反對。戰區部隊時刻保持高度戒備，隨時應對一切威脅挑釁。"},{"pid":"bab9c4ef7e512f552dc964c5ddc5e169d94bb1c7","tid":2422670,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"堅決保衛台海穩定。唔射爆佢正賣國賊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427efa6f6177602ed7d7e2e251cc1a8567fb2ba5","tid":2422670,"uid":36157,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"（普通話）<br />\n<br />\n立正！<br />\n脫～褲子！<br />\n再立正！<br />\n脫～底底！<br />\n立正！<br />\n弟弟立正！<br />\n打呀！<br />\n打他媽～的美軍！<br />\n打呀！"},{"pid":"fee73a200f21f7bfa5a4a4e2128a69a9fd2c4c2c","tid":2422670,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:13:48.000Z","msg":"幾時開火"},{"pid":"02d1c730bc2e1501b933e868c3e817b813b58932","tid":2422670,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":